      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Attempting to self-manage a condition requiring prescription blood thinners with specific dosages of supplements is extremely dangerous and poses a serious health risk. The therapeutic window of warfarin is narrow, meaning even small changes in factors like diet or supplements can dramatically affect your INR levels. Please trust your medical team and engage them in a collaborative discussion about your quality of life and medication concerns rather than trying to manage this critical condition on your own.",
      "source": "target",
